{"tid":853293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球霸美欺諗住踢丹比利出巴賽","createTime":"2018-10-08T13:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T13:44:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"588be43f0eec2739b212e15d9fe7b47e966b1fa8","tid":853293,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"Messi keen on Dembele exit from Barca<br />\n<br />\nCatalans to turn to Rabiot as replacement<br />\n<br />\nOusmane Dembele could be set to exit Barcelona as teammate Lionel Messi does not play well with him, reports Don Balon.<br />\n<br />\nThe Spanish champions will instead look to replace the Frenchman with Adrien Rabiot, who is preferred by the Argentina international.<br />\n<br />\nDembele was a member of France's World Cup winning squad this summer and was an unused substitution against Croatia in the final.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 球霸"},{"pid":"86dbe3f69399d61116eed8c3775658f6205d1f29","tid":853293,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"球霸（無世界盃）<br />\n<br />\n咁我普巴係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9bb99385881bd7ad180a26694c7ff3d90ea427","tid":853293,"uid":58811,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/211504_2eaf2829438dc7081e5a4ecdc0b1566e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F211504_2eaf2829438dc7081e5a4ecdc0b1566e.gif&h=eb13d598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n系"},{"pid":"8526d92b90db301f785c5fc5f58094e5cc0c5fb8","tid":853293,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"美欺<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/nintchdbpict0